{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775897235479,"sessionID":"ses_28448f185ffehh0S7VCtwI6VcR","part":{"id":"prt_d7bb94ff1001obLh46O0uWFdTn","messageID":"msg_d7bb8616e001PYrS8XVftfEKOJ","sessionID":"ses_28448f185ffehh0S7VCtwI6VcR","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-be252ac204f846b79e6a696a3e74cc94","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-039/proposal.md","content":"# AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n\n## 概述\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| AR | AR-039 |\n| Module | pkg |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n\n---\n\n## 1. Purpose (目的)\n\n为 `pkg/router`、`pkg/store`、`pkg/picod` 三个核心模块补充和完善单元测试，确保：\n\n- **代码质量保障**：通过测试覆盖关键业务逻辑，包括 HTTP 路由、JWT 认证、会话管理、存储操作、代码执行沙箱等核心功能\n- **回归测试支持**：建立稳定的测试基准，支持未来代码变更的安全验证\n- **边界条件覆盖**：补充现有测试未覆盖的边缘场景，如错误处理路径、并发安全性、资源泄漏检测\n- **测试基础设施完善**：提供 Mock 实现、测试辅助函数、Benchmark 测试等基础设施\n\n---\n\n## 2. Scope (范围)\n\n### 2.1 In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `pkg/router` 测试补充 | 补充 `handleInvoke` 错误分支测试、TLS 配置验证测试、并发请求压力测试 |\n| `pkg/store` 测试补充 | 补充 Valkey 存储实现测试、连接失败/重试测试、数据一致性测试 |\n| `pkg/picod` 测试补充 | 补充 `ExecuteHandler` 命令不存在测试、`FilesHandler` 权限边界测试、并发执行安全性测试 |\n| 测试辅助工具 | 完善 `MockStore`、`MockSessionManager`、`MockLogger` 等测试 Mock 实现 |\n| Benchmark 测试 | 为 JWT 签发/验证、存储操作、命令执行等高频操作添加性能基准测试 |\n\n### 2.2 Out of Scope\n\n| Item | Reason |\n|------|--------|\n| `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块测试 | 属于其他 AR 范围 |\n| `pkg/agentd` 模块测试 | 属于其他 AR 范围 |\n| 集成测试和端到端测试 | 本 AR 仅关注单元测试 |\n| 修改生产代码逻辑 | 仅添加测试，不修改业务实现 |\n\n---\n\n## 3. Impact Analysis (影响分析)\n\n### 3.1 新增文件\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `pkg/router/benchmark_test.go` | 路由处理性能基准测试 |\n| `pkg/store/benchmark_test.go` | 存储操作性能基准测试 |\n| `pkg/picod/benchmark_test.go` | PicoD 性能基准测试 |\n\n### 3.2 修改文件\n\n| File | Change |\n|------|--------|\n| `pkg/router/server_test.go` | 补充 `handleInvoke` 错误处理测试、并发请求测试 |\n| `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` | 补充 JWT Key 轮换测试、时钟偏差边界测试 |\n| `pkg/router/session_manager_test.go` | 补充网络超时测试、重试机制测试 |\n| `pkg/store/store_test.go` | 补充并发读写测试、连接池耗尽测试 |\n| `pkg/store/valkey_test.go` | 补充 Valkey 特定功能测试 |\n| `pkg/picod/picod_test.go` | 补充命令执行超时测试、大文件上传测试 |\n| `pkg/picod/auth_test.go` | 补充密钥轮换并发安全性测试 |\n\n### 3.3 Upstream Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Purpose |\n|------------|---------|\n| `github.com/stretchr/testify` | 测试断言和 Mock 框架 |\n| `github.com/alicebob/miniredis/v2` | Redis 内存模拟服务器 |\n| `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | HTTP 路由框架（测试模式） |\n| `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | JWT 测试辅助 |\n\n### 3.4 Downstream Consumers\n\n| Consumer | Usage |\n|----------|-------|\n| CI/CD Pipeline | 运行单元测试验证代码质量 |\n| 开发团队 | 本地开发时运行测试验证 |\n\n---\n\n## 4. Alternatives Considered (备选方案)\n\n### 4.1 Ginkgo/Gomega 测试框架\n\n**优点**：\n- 更丰富的 DSL 语法\n- 内置并行测试支持\n\n**缺点**：\n- 需要额外依赖引入\n- 与现有 `testing` + `testify` 风格不一致\n- 学习成本较高\n\n**决策**：不采用，继续使用标准 `testing` 包配合 `testify`\n\n### 4.2 真实 Redis/Valkey 实例测试\n\n**优点**：\n- 更真实的存储行为验证\n\n**缺点**：\n- 测试环境依赖外部服务\n- 测试运行速度慢\n- CI 环境配置复杂\n\n**决策**：不采用，继续使用 `miniredis` 内存模拟\n\n### 4.3 集成测试替代部分单元测试\n\n**优点**：\n- 覆盖真实交互场景\n\n**缺点**：\n- 测试范围超出 AR 定义\n- 运行时间更长\n- 调试困难\n\n**决策**：不采用，严格限定为单元测试范围\n\n---\n\n## 5. Risks\n\n| Risk | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|\n| 测试覆盖率不足遗漏边界条件 | 使用 `go test -cover` 分析覆盖率，针对性补充 |\n| Mock 实现与真实行为不一致 | Mock 实现基于实际接口定义，定期同步更新 |\n| 测试运行时间过长影响 CI | Benchmark 测试独立文件，单元测试保持快速执行 |\n| 并发测试不稳定性 | 使用 `t.Parallel()` 和适当的同步机制 |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Implementation Checklist\n\n- [ ] 补充 `pkg/router/server_test.go` 错误处理路径测试\n- [ ] 补充 `pkg/router/session_manager_test.go` 网络错误测试\n- [ ] 补充 `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` 密钥轮换边界测试\n- [ ] 补充 `pkg/store/store_test.go` 并发操作测试\n- [ ] 补充 `pkg/store/valkey_test.go` Valkey 特性测试\n- [ ] 补充 `pkg/picod/picod_test.go` 命令执行边界测试\n- [ ] 补充 `pkg/picod/auth_test.go` 并发密钥更新测试\n- [ ] 创建 `pkg/router/benchmark_test.go`\n- [ ] 创建 `pkg/store/benchmark_test.go`\n- [ ] 创建 `pkg/picod/benchmark_test.go`\n- [ ] 运行 `go test -cover ./pkg/router ./pkg/store ./pkg/picod` 验证覆盖率\n- [ ] 确保所有测试通过 `go test ./pkg/...`\n\n---\n\n## 7. References\n\n- [client-go library spec](../deployment/client-go.md)\n- Go Testing Best Practices: https://go.dev/doc/tutorial/add-a-test\n- testify Documentation: https://github.com/stretchr/testify\n- miniredis Documentation: https://github.com/alicebob/miniredis"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/cmd/agentd/main.go\">\nERROR [8:2] \"time\" imported and not used\n</diagnostics>","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/store/store.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/store/store_test.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":284,"character":5},"end":{"line":284,"character":24}},"severity":4,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/modernize#rangeint"},"source":"rangeint","message":"for loop can be modernized using range over int"},{"range":{"start":{"line":384,"character":5},"end":{"line":384,"character":24}},"severity":4,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/modernize#rangeint"},"source":"rangeint","message":"for loop can be modernized using range over int"}],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/picod/picod_test.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":758,"character":21},"end":{"line":758,"character":32}},"severity":4,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/modernize#any"},"source":"any","message":"interface{} can be replaced by any"},{"range":{"start":{"line":1077,"character":5},"end":{"line":1077,"character":28}},"severity":4,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"hre